    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Domnus <persName
                            key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arichis</persName> piissimus atque
                        excellentissimus <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> gentis Langubardorum,
                        divino premonitus nutu, offero in <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            key="#Fisheries #Churches"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancte
                            Sophie</orgName> quam a fundamentis edificavi, pro redemptione anime meę
                        seu pro salvatione gentis nostre et patrie integram <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >piscationem</rs> sacri nostri palatii in <rs key="#Sea">mare</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Sea #Fisheries #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/2836"
                            >Sipontina</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Size">passos trecentos</rs>, ex una parte <rs key="#Fines"
                            >fine</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Fines #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3439"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> Sancti Vincentii</orgName> et de
                        alia parte fine <orgName key="#Fines #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3440"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                            Sancti Petri</orgName>; nec non et concessimus in eodem loco <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3438"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancte
                            Eufimię</orgName> cum integre <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs>
                        sacri nostri palatii; et insuper in eodem monasterio concessimus in predicto
                        loco <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Condomae"
                            >condome</rs> tres <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ad piscandum et
                            ad salem faciendum</rs> in eodem <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >pantano</rs>: <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Teroaldus">Teroaldu</name> cum uxore et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus et <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Anseramus">Anseramu</name> cum uxore et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> que regitur per <name
                            ref="Garoaldus">Garoaldum</name> cum uxore et filiis et omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus, qui fuerunt de <rs key="#Subactio">subactione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus #Subactio" ref="#people/3449"
                            >Hermerissi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldio</rs> nostro seu et <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3415"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ecclesia</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3417" key="#Gai #Fiscal_property">Sancte
                                Reparate</placeName></orgName> que posita est in <geogName
                            key="#Gai #Fiscal_property" ref="#estates/3407"><rs key="#Gai">gaio</rs>
                            nostro Fecline</geogName> et circa ipsa ecclesia largiti sumus in
                        monasterio Sancte Sophię <rs key="#Landed_possessions">territoria</rs><rs
                            key="#Size"> modia centum</rs> quantum presbyter ipsius ecclesię <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation">sine palatii
                            concessionem tenebat</rs>. Quod vero <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma #Offersio/donatio">preceptus
                            oblationis</rs> ex iussione et dictatus nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3410">Lopoald</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> in filicissimo' <rs
                            key="#Palatium">palatio</rs> in anno septimo decimo, mensi novembrio per
                        indictione tertiam decimam. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
